OL,3,CParents and grandparents in Cornwall
OL,4,Cplead for Government help on Budget day
OL,6,FCaroline says the price of everything
OL,7,Fis still going up and she wants to see
OL,8,Fa further cut to inflation.
OL,10,F"It's the basics, the essentials
OL,11,Freally," she said. "If the price of
OL,12,Fthe essentials could come down, I
OL,13,Fthink that would really help families
OL,14,Flike myself."
OL,16,F'I am embarrassed'
OL,18,FJenny Adamson, who was visiting
OL,19,FNewquay library with her
OL,20,Fgrandchildren, wants more help for
OL,21,Folder people.
