OL,3,CParents and grandparents in Cornwall
OL,4,Cplead for Government help on Budget day
OL,6,F"I was brought up in the '50s and
OL,7,F'60s, after the war, when nobody had
OL,8,Fany money. We lived on very little. I
OL,9,Fnever bought any clothes until I was
OL,10,Fin employment until 23.
OL,12,F"We went to jumble sales, cut them up
OL,13,Fand made our own dresses. So I learned
OL,14,Fto live on very little.
OL,16,F"I've worked all my life, earned
OL,17,Fpensions, and I'm embarrassed by the
OL,18,Famount they give pensioners.
