OL,3,CParents and grandparents in Cornwall
OL,4,Cplead for Government help on Budget day
OL,6,F"They have put another #500 in this
OL,7,Fwinter to all pensioners. Some
OL,8,Fpensioners are very poor, but because
OL,9,Fof the way I was brought up I've
OL,10,Falways managed to build up pensions
OL,11,Fand have money there. But it's not the
OL,12,Fsame for everybody."
OL,14,F'People are suffering'
OL,16,FMum Martine, who did not want to give
OL,17,Fher surname, said she sometimes faces
OL,18,Fa choice between taking a shower and
OL,19,Fputting her heating on and wants the
OL,20,FGovernment to put more money into
OL,21,Fhousing.
