OL,3,CParents and grandparents in Cornwall
OL,4,Cplead for Government help on Budget day
OL,6,F"Things are really tight," she said.
OL,8,F"Rent is incredibly expensive, and
OL,9,Fthere are not the jobs to sustain a
OL,10,Fdecent standard of living here.
OL,12,F"Our electric is about #10 a day, food
OL,13,Fhas gone up, just life has gone up
OL,14,Fwhich is not sustainable anymore.
OL,15,FPeople are suffering."
