OL,3,CParents and grandparents in Cornwall
OL,4,Cplead for Government help on Budget day
OL,6,FEstate agent Jonathan Lawson, who is
OL,7,Fdirector of the Newquay Business
OL,8,FImprovement District, said: "The basic
OL,9,Fproblem with the housing market is a
OL,10,Flack of supply. We are not building
OL,11,Fenough homes."
OL,13,FVeryan Palmer, who runs Newquay's
OL,14,FHeadland Hotel, wants the Government
OL,15,Fto cut VAT rates for hospitality
OL,16,Fbusinesses.
OL,18,F"It would help businesses to survive,"
OL,19,Fshe said.
